[
    {
        "index": 1,
        "start_time": 6735,
        "end_time": 9356,
        "text": "Ani stands before a large golden scale"
    },
    {
        "index": 2,
        "start_time": 9356,
        "end_time": 12879,
        "text": "where the jackal-headed god\nAnubis is weighing his heart"
    },
    {
        "index": 3,
        "start_time": 12879,
        "end_time": 15907,
        "text": "against a pure ostrich feather."
    },
    {
        "index": 4,
        "start_time": 15907,
        "end_time": 17696,
        "text": "Ani was a real person,"
    },
    {
        "index": 5,
        "start_time": 17696,
        "end_time": 20480,
        "text": "a scribe from the Egyptian city\nof Thebes"
    },
    {
        "index": 6,
        "start_time": 20480,
        "end_time": 23672,
        "text": "who lived in the 13th century BCE."
    },
    {
        "index": 7,
        "start_time": 23672,
        "end_time": 27319,
        "text": "And depicted here is a scene\nfrom his Book of the Dead,"
    },
    {
        "index": 8,
        "start_time": 27319,
        "end_time": 32700,
        "text": "a 78-foot papyrus scroll\ndesigned to help him attain immortality."
    },
    {
        "index": 9,
        "start_time": 32700,
        "end_time": 37289,
        "text": "Such funerary texts were originally\nwritten only for Pharaohs,"
    },
    {
        "index": 10,
        "start_time": 37289,
        "end_time": 39891,
        "text": "but with time, the Egyptians came\nto believe"
    },
    {
        "index": 11,
        "start_time": 39891,
        "end_time": 43031,
        "text": "regular people could also reach\nthe afterlife"
    },
    {
        "index": 12,
        "start_time": 43031,
        "end_time": 46870,
        "text": "if they succeeded in the passage."
    },
    {
        "index": 13,
        "start_time": 46870,
        "end_time": 49601,
        "text": "Ani&#39;s epic journey begins with his death."
    },
    {
        "index": 14,
        "start_time": 49601,
        "end_time": 52462,
        "text": "His body is mummified by a team of priests"
    },
    {
        "index": 15,
        "start_time": 52462,
        "end_time": 55562,
        "text": "who remove every organ except the heart,"
    },
    {
        "index": 16,
        "start_time": 55562,
        "end_time": 59122,
        "text": "the seat of emotion, memory, \nand intelligence."
    },
    {
        "index": 17,
        "start_time": 59122,
        "end_time": 61721,
        "text": "It&#39;s then stuffed with a salt\ncalled natron"
    },
    {
        "index": 18,
        "start_time": 61721,
        "end_time": 64901,
        "text": "and wrapped in resin-soaked linen."
    },
    {
        "index": 19,
        "start_time": 64901,
        "end_time": 68880,
        "text": "In addition, the wrappings are woven\nwith charms for protection"
    },
    {
        "index": 20,
        "start_time": 68880,
        "end_time": 73792,
        "text": "and topped with a heart scarab amulet\nthat will prove important later on."
    },
    {
        "index": 21,
        "start_time": 73792,
        "end_time": 78931,
        "text": "The goal of the two-month process\nis to preserve Ani&#39;s body as an ideal form"
    },
    {
        "index": 22,
        "start_time": 78931,
        "end_time": 82294,
        "text": "with which his spirit \ncan eventually reunite."
    },
    {
        "index": 23,
        "start_time": 82294,
        "end_time": 86973,
        "text": "But first, that spirit must pass\nthrough the duat, or underworld."
    },
    {
        "index": 24,
        "start_time": 86973,
        "end_time": 89032,
        "text": "This is a realm of vast caverns,"
    },
    {
        "index": 25,
        "start_time": 89032,
        "end_time": 90122,
        "text": "lakes of fire,"
    },
    {
        "index": 26,
        "start_time": 90122,
        "end_time": 91580,
        "text": "and magical gates,"
    },
    {
        "index": 27,
        "start_time": 91580,
        "end_time": 93680,
        "text": "all guarded by fearsome beasts -"
    },
    {
        "index": 28,
        "start_time": 93680,
        "end_time": 97654,
        "text": "snakes, crocodiles,\nand half-human monstrosities"
    },
    {
        "index": 29,
        "start_time": 97654,
        "end_time": 100751,
        "text": "with names like &quot;he who dances in blood.&quot;"
    },
    {
        "index": 30,
        "start_time": 100751,
        "end_time": 104233,
        "text": "To make things worse, Apep, the serpent\ngod of destruction,"
    },
    {
        "index": 31,
        "start_time": 104233,
        "end_time": 108812,
        "text": "lurks in the shadows waiting to swallow\nAni&#39;s soul."
    },
    {
        "index": 32,
        "start_time": 108812,
        "end_time": 110602,
        "text": "Fortunately, Ani is prepared"
    },
    {
        "index": 33,
        "start_time": 110602,
        "end_time": 114053,
        "text": "with the magic contained \nwithin his book of the dead."
    },
    {
        "index": 34,
        "start_time": 114053,
        "end_time": 116083,
        "text": "Like other Egyptians who could afford it,"
    },
    {
        "index": 35,
        "start_time": 116083,
        "end_time": 121434,
        "text": "Ani customized his scroll to include\nthe particular spells, prayers, and codes"
    },
    {
        "index": 36,
        "start_time": 121434,
        "end_time": 124994,
        "text": "he thought his spirit might need."
    },
    {
        "index": 37,
        "start_time": 124994,
        "end_time": 126455,
        "text": "Equipped with this arsenal,"
    },
    {
        "index": 38,
        "start_time": 126455,
        "end_time": 128564,
        "text": "our hero traverses the obstacles,"
    },
    {
        "index": 39,
        "start_time": 128564,
        "end_time": 130536,
        "text": "repels the monsters&#39; acts,"
    },
    {
        "index": 40,
        "start_time": 130536,
        "end_time": 132733,
        "text": "and stealthily avoids Apep"
    },
    {
        "index": 41,
        "start_time": 132733,
        "end_time": 138343,
        "text": "to reach the Hall of Ma&#39;at,\ngoddess of truth and justice."
    },
    {
        "index": 42,
        "start_time": 138343,
        "end_time": 140763,
        "text": "Here, Ani faces his final challenge."
    },
    {
        "index": 43,
        "start_time": 140763,
        "end_time": 143933,
        "text": "He is judged by 42 assessor gods"
    },
    {
        "index": 44,
        "start_time": 143933,
        "end_time": 147964,
        "text": "who must be convinced \nthat he has lived a righteous life."
    },
    {
        "index": 45,
        "start_time": 147964,
        "end_time": 149714,
        "text": "Ani approaches each one,"
    },
    {
        "index": 46,
        "start_time": 149714,
        "end_time": 151075,
        "text": "addressing them by name,"
    },
    {
        "index": 47,
        "start_time": 151075,
        "end_time": 154354,
        "text": "and declaring a sin he has not committed."
    },
    {
        "index": 48,
        "start_time": 154354,
        "end_time": 158835,
        "text": "Among these negative confessions,\nor declarations of innocence,"
    },
    {
        "index": 49,
        "start_time": 158835,
        "end_time": 161566,
        "text": "he proclaims that he has not made\nanyone cry,"
    },
    {
        "index": 50,
        "start_time": 161566,
        "end_time": 163245,
        "text": "is not an eavesdropper,"
    },
    {
        "index": 51,
        "start_time": 163245,
        "end_time": 165575,
        "text": "and has not polluted the water."
    },
    {
        "index": 52,
        "start_time": 165575,
        "end_time": 169134,
        "text": "But did Ani really live \nsuch a perfect life?"
    },
    {
        "index": 53,
        "start_time": 169134,
        "end_time": 173425,
        "text": "Not quite, but that&#39;s where \nthe heart scarab amulet comes in."
    },
    {
        "index": 54,
        "start_time": 173425,
        "end_time": 177865,
        "text": "It&#39;s inscribed with the words,\n&quot;Do not stand as a witness against me,&quot;"
    },
    {
        "index": 55,
        "start_time": 177865,
        "end_time": 181034,
        "text": "precisely so Ani&#39;s heart \ndoesn&#39;t betray him"
    },
    {
        "index": 56,
        "start_time": 181034,
        "end_time": 183754,
        "text": "by recalling the time he listened\nto his neighbors fight"
    },
    {
        "index": 57,
        "start_time": 183754,
        "end_time": 187586,
        "text": "or washed his feet in the Nile."
    },
    {
        "index": 58,
        "start_time": 187586,
        "end_time": 191774,
        "text": "Now, it&#39;s Ani&#39;s moment of truth,\nthe weighing of the heart."
    },
    {
        "index": 59,
        "start_time": 191774,
        "end_time": 195956,
        "text": "If his heart is heavier than the feather,\nweighed down by Ani&#39;s wrongdoings,"
    },
    {
        "index": 60,
        "start_time": 195956,
        "end_time": 199199,
        "text": "it&#39;ll be devoured \nby the monstrous Ammit,"
    },
    {
        "index": 61,
        "start_time": 199199,
        "end_time": 203285,
        "text": "part crocodile, part leopard, \npart hippopotamus,"
    },
    {
        "index": 62,
        "start_time": 203285,
        "end_time": 206756,
        "text": "and Ani will cease to exist forever."
    },
    {
        "index": 63,
        "start_time": 206756,
        "end_time": 208466,
        "text": "But Ani is in luck."
    },
    {
        "index": 64,
        "start_time": 208466,
        "end_time": 210104,
        "text": "His heart is judged pure."
    },
    {
        "index": 65,
        "start_time": 210104,
        "end_time": 215196,
        "text": "Ra, the sun god, takes him to Osiris,\ngod of the underworld,"
    },
    {
        "index": 66,
        "start_time": 215196,
        "end_time": 219197,
        "text": "who gives him final approval to enter\nthe afterlife."
    },
    {
        "index": 67,
        "start_time": 219197,
        "end_time": 221917,
        "text": "In the endless and lush field of reeds,"
    },
    {
        "index": 68,
        "start_time": 221917,
        "end_time": 224255,
        "text": "Ani meets his deceased parents."
    },
    {
        "index": 69,
        "start_time": 224255,
        "end_time": 229065,
        "text": "Here, there is no sadness, pain, or anger,\nbut there is work to be done."
    },
    {
        "index": 70,
        "start_time": 229065,
        "end_time": 232315,
        "text": "Like everyone else, Ani must cultivate\na plot of land,"
    },
    {
        "index": 71,
        "start_time": 232315,
        "end_time": 238046,
        "text": "which he does with the help of a Shabti\ndoll that had been placed in his tomb."
    },
    {
        "index": 72,
        "start_time": 238046,
        "end_time": 241636,
        "text": "Today, the Papyrus of Ani resides\nin the British Museum,"
    },
    {
        "index": 73,
        "start_time": 241636,
        "end_time": 244405,
        "text": "where it has been since 1888."
    },
    {
        "index": 74,
        "start_time": 244405,
        "end_time": 248626,
        "text": "Only Ani, if anyone, knows what really\nhappened after his death."
    },
    {
        "index": 75,
        "start_time": 248626,
        "end_time": 250408,
        "text": "But thanks to his Book of the Dead,"
    },
    {
        "index": 76,
        "start_time": 250408,
        "end_time": 254377,
        "text": "we can imagine him happily tending\nhis crops for all eternity."
    }
]